<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥١٥٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7010">يَحْيَى: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6792">وَكِيعٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2521">أَبِي حَازِمٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2676">سَهْلِ بْنِ سَعْدٍ</a> <span class="c2">«أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ لِرَجُلٍ: تَزَوَّجْ وَلَوْ بِخَاتَمٍ مِنْ حَدِيدٍ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>